<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="description" content="">

<link href="../assets/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
      .bd-placeholder-img {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        text-anchor: middle;
        -webkit-user-select: none;
        -moz-user-select: none;
        user-select: none;
      }

      media (min-width: 768px) {
        .bd-placeholder-img-lg {
          font-size: 3.5rem;
        }
      }

      .b-example-divider {
        height: 3rem;
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, .1);
        border: solid rgba(0, 0, 0, .15);
        border-width: 1px 0;
        box-shadow: inset 0 .5em 1.5em rgba(0, 0, 0, .1), inset 0 .125em .5em rgba(0, 0, 0, .15);
      }

      .b-example-vr {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        width: 1.5rem;
        height: 100vh;
      }

      .bi {
        vertical-align: -.125em;
        fill: currentColor;
      }

      .nav-scroller {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        height: 2.75rem;
        overflow-y: hidden;
      }

      .nav-scroller .nav {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: nowrap;
        padding-bottom: 1rem;
        margin-top: -1px;
        overflow-x: auto;
        text-align: center;
        white-space: nowrap;
        -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
      }
    </style>

    
  </head>
  <body>
    
<main>

  <div class="container py-4">
    <div class="p-5 mb-4 bg-light rounded-3">
      <div class="container-fluid py-5">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Oratio</h1>
        <p class="col-md-8 fs-4">This system revolutionizes managing prayer intentions. Join the revolution and register for FREE today</p>
        <a asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Register</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row align-items-md-stretch">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="h-100 p-5 text-bg-dark rounded-3">
          <h2>Leave the administration to us, develop a relationship with God</h2>
          <p>Thanks to the built-in calendar, you can easily manage your intentions. Find a mass and add your intention to it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="h-100 p-5 bg-light border rounded-3">
          <h2>100% warranty on data and security.</h2>
          <p>Experience peace of mind with our 100% warranty on data and security. That's why we guarantee that all data stored and processed with us will be completely secure and protected from unauthorized access or breaches. Trust us to keep your data safe and secure.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
